LINK: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/608945602/grammy-nominee-geoffrey-keezers-new-jazz-album
The Geoffrey Keezer Trio is working on 'On My Way To You,' an exciting new album of jazz covers and originals, and damn if these things aren't crazy expensive to make. So Geoffrey and the lads are hoping you can help defray the costs of this magical -- yet magically expensive -- undertaking via this Kickstarter campaign. If you're looking to simply purchase the album at cost, this would be the place to do it! Or if you'd enjoy shelling out a bit more for some sweet, sweet perks, there'd certainly be no objections on this end.
